# MLModelStructure.neuralNetwork(_:)

**Case**

Represents a NeuralNetwork model, the associated value is the structure of the NeuralNetwork.

## Declaration

```swift
case neuralNetwork(MLModelStructure.NeuralNetwork)
```

## Model structures

- **MLModelStructure.NeuralNetwork**: A struct representing the structure of a NeuralNetwork model..
- **MLModelStructure.pipeline(_:)**: Represents a Pipeline model, the associated value is the structure of the Pipeline.
- **MLModelStructure.Pipeline**: A struct representing the structure of a Pipeline model..
- **MLModelStructure.program(_:)**: Represents a MLProgram model. the associated value is the structure of the Program.
- **MLModelStructure.Program**: A struct representing the structure of an ML Program model.
- **MLModelStructure.unsupported**: Represents an unsupported model.
